{"tid":1331793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊岳橋：：若再有香港人獲得其他地方的庇護，會影響香港的國際聲譽，因為代表外界質疑香港的律政司有否作出公平檢控。","createTime":"2019-07-19T05:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T13:17:51.000Z","uid":222189,"like":287,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"a0acdcaaf0e6ad7efd0b79cca85408b849c2f68b","tid":1331793,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469182-20190719.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469182-20190719.htm&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=5e534d66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469182-20190719.htm&h=db60d69e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469182-20190719.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有傳媒報道，多名香港反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威者，自從7月1日衝擊立法會後到了台灣，希望尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋表示，任何人尋求其他地方的政治庇護，要視乎申請人在原居地是否因為政治原因，受到檢控或有可能受檢控，並是否有機會獲得不公平審訊。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，若再有香港人獲得其他地方的庇護，會影響香港的國際聲譽，因為代表外界質疑香港的律政司有否作出公平檢控。"},{"pid":"3c2750826a12ff31e3b5fa3f03710d26e59a823f","tid":1331793,"uid":31237,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8CzHJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8CzHJ8.jpg&h=308e5fb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8afb46d4c32a67b1c765d5ca73d31dbae0b20957","tid":1331793,"uid":75156,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因為代表外界質疑香港的律政司有否作出公平檢控。</span>紅字再罰抄一次 我諗會開心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d0b815a5dab6691a29e39d266ae6a85b0226ac","tid":1331793,"uid":60434,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"得喇樓豬又開post  知你咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas